title: Old Cahto Peak rain bucket kicks bucket
description: Old tipping bucket rain gage is reporting constant 0.25 mm rain every sample interval.  The new rain gauge is responding normally.  This may be a function of a light snow preventing the old instrument from functioning.  The newer one has a heating element.   incident report migrated from SensorDB.
